发质和头发长度的女性有更舒适的选择。 在过去几年，其他军队也逐步改变了对女性军人发型的规定，其中就有美国海军。2018 年，美国海军表示，水兵在穿制服时可以扎马尾辫或盘成发髻。来源：环球网"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "279 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/441618494"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Im46Q+LWE1sglEAMaCDYwNDE1NDQwIJ7GyIAGMAo4igFAFXIJNDQxNjE4NDk0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "22_1611926226.7666528", "card_id": "Q_441447552", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 119}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "父母为什么不理解当代年轻人的绝望？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "当代年轻人幸福感越来越低，父母一辈为什么不理解？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-b79ebd6d60d4f7ad2e0baa1285ebe1a7_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "270 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/441447552"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Im46Q+LWE1sglEAMaCDYwMzc3NDY2IKGRxIAGMAY4iwNAFnIJNDQxNDQ3NTUyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "23_1611926226.766963", "card_id": "Q_441651301", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 48}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价「首批电竞本科生几乎没人从事电竞」？电竞专业有必要开设吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "1 月 28 日据报道，中国传媒大学数字娱乐专业学生表示：「班上就业情况特别好，但严格来讲没有从事电竞工作的同学。」大部分人进入互联网大厂或者游戏公司做游戏策划、运营类工作，其他同学会选择转行。多位同学反映，除一线大厂的电竞部门，大多数电竞公司起始薪资并不高。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-269cce24b143205505a1e05a72e0a9af_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "264 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/441651301"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Im46Q+LWE1sglEAMaCDYwNDIyNzI3IMikyYAGMAA4zwFAF3IJNDQxNjUxMzAxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "24_1611926226.767408", "card_id": "Q_441684451", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 31}, "t